{
  "texts": [
    "To preserve the information in the data, pooling layers are intentionally omitted.",
    "The self-attention mechanism can model the dependencies and aggregate features from inputs.",
    "Therefore, a stacking structure of self-attention mechanisms like Transformer (Vaswani et al., 2017) can achieve the functions of CNNs and RNNs without iterations.",
    "This provides a novel way for predictions to be made.",
    "In this study, we utilize the encoder structure of the Transformer (Vaswani et al., 2017), as depicted in Fig. 4c, to predict soil moisture."
  ]
}